Author: wookie#7663
Content: Thought I'd start a Pirate trivia of the day: Pirates didn’t always bury (hodl) their treasure. Some pirates didn’t bury their treasure right away because they wanted their share of the loot beforehand (selling early). And a pirate’s treasure didn’t always include gold (BTC) or silver; most of it was food, lumber, cloth, and animal hides.
